# menu.db --- Menu definition for flu.sh v1.1
# Format: Category|Subcategory|Label|action_id
# Lines starting with # are comments. Empty lines are ignored.
# Action IDs map 1:1 to module script filenames in modules/<action_id>.sh

# -- Diagnostics --
Diagnostics|System|> Status Check|status_check
Diagnostics|System|> Compare With Latest|status_check_compare
Diagnostics|Updates|> Upgrade All Tools|upgrade_all

# -- AI Tools --
AI Tools|OpenCode|> Install OpenCode|install_opencode
AI Tools|OpenCode|x Remove OpenCode|remove_opencode
AI Tools|GSD (Rokicool)|> Install GSD (Rokicool)|install_gsd_rokicool
AI Tools|Open GSD|> Install gsd-core|install_gsd_core
AI Tools|Open GSD|x Remove gsd-core|remove_gsd_core
AI Tools|Open GSD|> Install gsd-pi|install_gsd_pi
AI Tools|Open GSD|x Remove gsd-pi|remove_gsd_pi
AI Tools|Open GSD|> Install gsd-browser|install_gsd_browser
AI Tools|Open GSD|x Remove gsd-browser|remove_gsd_browser
AI Tools|Open GSD|> Install all Open GSD|install_gsd_all
AI Tools|Open GSD|x Remove all Open GSD|remove_gsd_all
AI Tools|Hermes Agent|> Install Hermes Agent|install_hermes_agent
AI Tools|OpenChamber|> Install OpenChamber|install_openchamber

