# -- Shell --
Shell|Prompts|+ Fancy Prompt (Purple-Pink)|create_fancy_prompt
Shell|Prompts|x Remove Fancy Prompt (Purple-Pink)|remove_fancy_prompt
Shell|Prompts|+ Fancy Prompt (Shades of Blue)|create_fancy_prompt_blue
